 sure and tighter central-bank policy.\n\n• Why traders care: Wage grow
 th can feed into inflation and is closely watched by central banks.\n\n
 • Frequency: Monthly or quarterly depending on release.\n\n• Notes: 
 Strong wages can be positive for consumers but can also increase inflati
 on pressure.\n\n• Acronyms: WPI = Wage Price Index.\n\nOfficial source
 : https://www.abs.gov.au/release-calendar/future-releases/202608\n\nExpl
