 rice Index.\n\nOfficial source: https://www.abs.gov.au/release-calendar/
 future-releases/202608\n\nExplainer:\n• What it is: Wage Price Index /
  Average Earnings\n\n• Measures: Change in wages and earnings.\n\n• 
 Usual market effect: Higher-than-forecast wage growth can be bullish for
  the local currency if traders expect stronger inflation pressure and ti
 ghter central-bank policy.\n\n• Why traders care: Wage growth can feed
  into inflation and is closely watched by central banks.\n\n• Frequenc
 y: Monthly or quarterly depending on release.\n\n• Notes: Strong wages
  can be positive for consumers but can also increase inflation pressure.
