 P is the broadest measure of economic growth and helps traders judge whe
 ther the economy is accelerating or slowing.\n\n• Frequency: Quarterly
 \, with revisions.\n\n• Notes: GDP can be backward-looking\, so market
 s often react more strongly when the result changes the outlook for cent
